      <div class="main-content">
        <h1>History of New Grove</h1>
        <h2>Early Settlement</h2>
        <p>Founded as a river trading post in the early 1800s, New Grove grew quickly due to its strategic location.</p>

        <h2>Industrial Expansion</h2>
        <p>The late 19th century brought railroads, factories, and river docks, fueling rapid population growth.</p>

        <h2>Modern Era</h2>
        <p>Today, New Grove is a regional center for culture, education, and technology.</p>
